{"tid":1012984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋冇你哋諗咁差","createTime":"2019-02-08T04:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T11:18:04.000Z","uid":234495,"like":18,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"be6f13e8dc1e24535c7b805a24fed3270ab911bb","tid":1012984,"uid":234495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"呢排我上連登見到好多人話公屋又廢又幾衰，想借個機會平反一下。<br />\n（非公屋仔，借朋友a.c. post)<br />\n&middot;好多新型公屋其實無你地諗咁差，唔會話又黑社又白粉，只不過係一班冇咁有錢嘅人住<br />\n<br />\n&middot;去過新型公共屋邨，入面裝修仲好過我地私樓...<br />\n<br />\n&middot;住戶質素，大家都只喺香港人，唔好覺得自己比較高級，最多公屋有多啲&ldquo;新移民&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&middot;定型，唔好覺得每一個住公屋嘅都係28座阿俊， 其實無咁低層，公屋都有好多正常人， 唔好次次殺人放火都話係公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0536d97e16cd05a2625e22dc8cafd15a56820128","tid":1012984,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"家陣連公屋都唔見曬D MK仔<br />\n唔知走曬去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9444de0039524db895a7ba6bd9cd43026f490eab","tid":1012984,"uid":234495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0536d97e16cd05a2625e22dc8cafd15a56820128","tid":1012984,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"家陣連公屋都唔見曬D MK仔<br />\n唔知走曬去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"可能瞓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121a9a13d240169d546fb19f93cbe0697e3c1546","tid":1012984,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0536d97e16cd05a2625e22dc8cafd15a56820128","tid":1012984,"uid":8439,